function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

-- Reposition Donan towards lecturn
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorDonan, MARKER_DONAN_TURNTO)

	-- Stage Yorin to exit area and add gossip conv list
	--Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorYorin, MARKER_YORIN_WALKTO, "npc_walk", true)
	Hydra.QActorFollowPathDynamicSpeed(actorYorin, spline_Yorin_WalkTo, "npc_walk", false)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorYorin, MARKER_YORIN_WALKTO)
	--Hydra.QActorAnimAndNewIdle(actorYorin, s_POWER_HORSE, s_POWER_HORSE)
	Hydra.QActorSetConversationList(actorYorin, s_CONVLIST_YORIN)

	-- Checked in condition QST_Scos_EldhaimeKeep_Donan.  If this variable is set, Donan will be visible.  Variable is cleared
	-- when the instance closes or when Donan enters the Estate during that quest.
	Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag("QST_Scos_EldhaimeKeep_Donan")

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Play short looping line every few seconds until players start cinematic
	Hydra.Wait(15.0)
	
	if not bCutsceneStarted then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convoDonanLoop, actorDonan, actorYorin)
	end
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Disable looped conversation
	bCutsceneStarted = true
end
